{"tid":2181912,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[預左比人屌] 請大家可唔可以對準敵人,試下講\"加油咩都試下\"而唔係\"有撚用咩\". 有錯就認,認左大家扶返起繼續前行","createTime":"2020-08-31T03:00:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-01T06:06:25.000Z","uid":179775,"like":81,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"bcf764cbc9e3013f75d53a3508f396fc96036149","tid":2181912,"uid":179775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T03:00:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有14年既味道<br />\n真係好驚<br />\n<br />\n最驚唔係驚輸比港共恐怖份子.......最驚既係失敗係自己手上面<br />\n如果繼續過唔成功都甘心<br />\n但輸係自己手上你地甘心嗎"},{"pid":"46b2b30a2f7ffd9a8a22192d74b741bb7d9bb226","tid":2181912,"uid":232766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T03:00:47.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"12cac6bdb85bc3cff04378f942911b1ffdcd3647","tid":2181912,"uid":232766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T03:00:58.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"363e73211f50e7eaf85925952758cd41f5e2100e","tid":2181912,"uid":65074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T03:01:31.000Z","msg":"咩都試下"},{"pid":"4735637963dd78118375c497e3b7b641425c4e94","tid":2181912,"uid":232766,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T03:03:59.000Z","msg":"比起 14 年，分化、放負手段近乎一樣，但尤幸民眾（連登仔、Facebook 人, etc.）「免疫」能力似乎強咗好多，但仍需要時刻警醒，唔好重蹈覆轍。"},{"pid":"52bec3d249d6a6c4ad315b90e99bf3d2cef8fab6","tid":2181912,"uid":179775,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T03:05:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />膳心係一個開始<br />\n佢係錯有唔岩....不過係咪要追殺到收皮呢<br />\n<br />\n龍門當日都比人屌到變藍<br />\n但好在佢堅持<br />\n<br />\n到最後咪還左佢自己清白<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有時試下互信....唔係講到咁白<br />\n好似今日已經有幾個post追緊大J<br />\n明顯有心人.......老實...一個90萬YOUTUBER要R30萬水<br />\n唔表態....食曬2邊.....一定有廣告唔只30萬啦"},{"pid":"24b04ef00fb04ec083dc26d55f1e8a0e59b6cc2d","tid":2181912,"uid":69585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T03:06:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />對準敵人"},{"pid":"6598950b038db466ea6b84c1fa5c585a2bf22288","tid":2181912,"uid":179775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T03:09:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />大家明白  一唔團結好快就收皮<br />\n對家好想好想我地分化<br />\n<br />\n和勇不分係幾難對付<br />\n家下重有國際線"},{"pid":"4964151649b1cbc103cfdf98c51ef0e39c5b67bc","tid":2181912,"uid":84123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T03:09:10.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\">不分化<br />\n不篤灰<br />\n不割蓆</span><br />\n<br />\n我無補充"},{"pid":"518be78edbb37c6c1e131d09014edac317fad94a","tid":2181912,"uid":116645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T03:10:06.000Z","msg":"兄弟爬山"},{"pid":"c336c18c4d38d198d38fddadd1cd547fb0884274","tid":2181912,"uid":78612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T03:11:35.000Z","msg":"咩都話無用既人最撚無用<br />\n<br />\n咩都私怨行先既人最撚仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ecd5063c347d6bf884723825c0474cae660571b","tid":2181912,"uid":232766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T03:14:50.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"34f8de24045f34b80770c0f9b46c0e0375e95c03","tid":2181912,"uid":362431,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T03:17:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d359bc962563d8a33adcde1ac2a9c56b211912ed","tid":2181912,"uid":179775,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"34f8de24045f34b80770c0f9b46c0e0375e95c03","tid":2181912,"uid":362431,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score